te; trong danh s&aacute;ch của m&igrave;nh. Hiện tại, tựa game đ&atilde; ra mắt tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c hệ m&aacute;y PC, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, PlayStation 4, Xbox One v&agrave; Nintendo Switch v&agrave; đ&atilde; c&oacute; b&aacute;n tại&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">HALO</span>. N&agrave;o c&aacute;c gangster, nhanh ch&acirc;n đặt h&agrave;ng ngay để trải nghiệm một l&uacute;c 3 con game GTA hấp dẫn đang chờ đợi bạn.</p>','<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: inherit; background-color: #ffffff; border-width: 0px; width: 538.188px; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\'; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px !important; border-style: none !important; border-color: initial !important;\">\r\n<thead style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; background: #eeeeee; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px solid transparent; border-left: 0px solid transparent; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: middle; width: 518.188px;\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">TH&Ocirc;NG TIN GAME</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 14px; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: middle; width: 114px; border: 0px solid transparent;\">Thể loại</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 14px; border-top: 0px solid transparent; border-right: 0px solid transparent; border-bottom: 0px solid transparent; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: middle;\">Action Adventure</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>',NULL,'SWG906',NULL,NULL